getFullName() - Method in interface com.netcracker.edu.java.tasks.CurriculumVitae
Returns the full name i.e. the FIRST part of the CV text that satisfies the following criteria: full name consists of 2 or 3 words separated with a space (' '); each word has 2 or more characters; the first character of the word is upper-case Latin letter (alphabetic character); the last character of the word is either '.' or lower-case Latin letter; non-first and non-last characters of the word can be lower-case Latin letter only.
getLastName() - Method in interface com.netcracker.edu.java.tasks.CurriculumVitae
Returns the last name from the CV (the last word of CurriculumVitae.getFullName()).
getMiddleName() - Method in interface com.netcracker.edu.java.tasks.CurriculumVitae
Returns the middle name from the CV (the second word of CurriculumVitae.getFullName()) or null if the full name has two words only.
